lead_paragraph: Radamel Falcao netted a double to give Monaco a 3-0 win against CSKA Moscow as the principality side took a big step towards a last 16 spot in the Champions League on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Falcao on Target as Monaco Beat CSKA Moscow
